ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
Federal Public Sector Labour Relations and Employment Board Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of State (Federal Economic Development Agency for Southern Ontario) to be the Minister Referred to in Federal Public Sector Labour Relations and Employment Board Act and as the Minister for the Purposes of the Federal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-1142 of November 23, 2023; and (2) designating the Minister of STATE (FEDERAL ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AGENCY FOR SOUTHERN ONTARIO), who is not a member of the Treasury Board, to be the Minister for the purposes of the FEDERAL PUBLIC SECTOR LABOUR RELATIONS ACT.
